Ranger Help for: improve
========================

SYNTAX:      improve <str/dex/con/wis/int/chr/level/guild>
USAGE:       Any wilderness terrain.

SUMMARY:
Advance your stats or game level, or review automatic Ranger guild progress.
You must be in a wilderness area (not city, inside, or dock terrain).

  improve str/dex/con/int/wis/chr   Raise a stat (costs experience)
  improve level                      Raise game level (costs experience)
  improve guild                      Show combat-earned Ranger XP progress

Your guild level cannot exceed your game level. Use 'cost' to see current
prices and Ranger XP. You must set your primary terrain, secondary terrain,
and enemy species before Ranger XP can raise your guild level above 1.

